import {
  Box,
  Button,
  Container,
  Paper,
  TextField,
  Typography,
} from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";
import { FlexColCenter } from "../elements";

function SchoolForm(props) {
  const [state, setState] = useState({
    noOfStudents: null,
    totalClasses: null,
    expense: null,
    revenue: null,
    profit: null,
  });
  return (
    <>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
        <Paper
          variant="outlined"
          sx={{ my: { xs: 3, md: 6 }, p: { xs: 5, md: 3 } }}
        >
          <FlexColCenter>
            <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">
              Profit Calculator
            </Typography>
          </FlexColCenter>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="No. Of Students"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Total Classes"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Expense "
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Revenue"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <FlexColCenter mt={3}>
            <Button variant="contained">Calculate</Button>
          </FlexColCenter>
        </Paper>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}

export default SchoolForm;
